{"tid":410973,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"20:35【真・哥斯拉 / 新哥斯拉 シン・ゴジラ 2016】","createTime":"2017-09-23T12:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T14:51:50.000Z","uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b36b8637bcc583d3a4c01e864f229a0a775bf1","tid":410973,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.simbla.com%2F871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a%2Fiusee&d=mX%2FGsdV%2BQFUXKbLb%2Fr71B7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=aa24016a\" target=\"_blank\">http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee</a><br />\n<br />\n　　毫無征兆的一天，日本東京灣突然冒出大量水蒸氣，與之相伴海底隧道則發生崩塌事故。政府方面迅速召開緊急會議，商討原因與對策，其中內閣官房副長官矢口蘭堂（長谷川博己 飾）獨辟蹊徑，懷疑和某種未知生物有關，卻反遭同儕嘲笑。結果事實勝於雄辯，不久後巨大的怪物登陸，對城區展開大肆破壞。在這一過程中，它以詭異的速度進化，隨後又突然止步，返回大海。利用短暫的間隙，矢口作為主導成立了&ldquo;巨大不明生物災害對策本部&rdquo;，網羅了數名公務員中的異類加盟。漸漸地他們弄清了怪物的生物構造和產生原因。 <br />\n　　當被命名為&ldquo;哥斯拉&rdquo;的怪物再度登陸，一場都市保衛戰正式打響&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-tcPuyGZ4dRA/WERCIjpH8QI/AAAAAAAAuW8/m6jtaEac5RAc-qwgclpZtjrF46DQrvmzwCLcB/s1600/16120785.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-tcPuyGZ4dRA%2FWERCIjpH8QI%2FAAAAAAAAuW8%2Fm6jtaEac5RAc-qwgclpZtjrF46DQrvmzwCLcB%2Fs1600%2F16120785.jpg&h=7952946c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cd6b4ee07f4c6a2a44d3cc0f36af226fe400131","tid":410973,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"31dfbf56eb5956ddd8bd1f216de9364898b08cf7","tid":410973,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"0d9e74ad26d8ca6ef77e7016b47a827dcaf6feb1","tid":410973,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"6b5cb0d17ce88b3231d798327495f8bad41